#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:1 trade
msgid "Operator：创建与基本配置"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:3 trade
msgid "Operator 是 qteasy 中策略的容器与调度器，负责在回测或实盘中按既定频率与时间点运行策略并输出统一格式的信号。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:5 trade
msgid "创建 Operator"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:7 trade
msgid ""
"使用 ``qt.Operator()`` 创建，可传入策略列表及 "
"``signal_type``、``run_freq``、``run_timing`` 等："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:19 trade
msgid "添加策略"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:21 trade
msgid ""
"**add_strategy(stg, run_freq=None, run_timing=None)**：添加单个策略，可指定该策略的 "
"``run_freq``/``run_timing``，与已有相同则归入同一 Group，否则新建 Group。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:22 trade
msgid ""
"**add_strategies(stg_list, run_freq=None, run_timing=None)**：批量添加，同样按 "
"``run_freq``/``run_timing`` 归组。"
msgstr ""

